title: Rino's Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Western, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Many of the dishes can easily be made vegetarian or vegan, simply by asking the server. Located within The House (formerly The Nisbett Inn), this cafe/pub offers a full cafe menu as well as a daily changing lunch/brunch menu. Uses locally produced food. Catering.
